Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:00.48,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:120487,120487}Metropolitan Entertainment approached Maya, who has just entered high school, about an audition for "The Miracle Worker."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:07.09,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:127093,127093}Maya declines out of fear of losing to her rival, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:12.06,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:132065,132065}Tsukikage threatens to expel Maya from Tsukikage Theater unless she gets the role of Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:27.23,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141224,147230}{\an5\pos(766,680)\fscy95\blur1\fad(0,0)}—Episode 18—\NThe Challenge of Helen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148915,148915}Metropolitan Entertainment has chosen you five as the candidates for the role of Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156189,156189}Shiratori Reina,\Nfrom Kaze Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159392,159392}Hayakawa Akiko,\Nfrom Tenma Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162362,162362}We recognize both of your achievements on TV series.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166266,166266}Kanaya Emi, who is a member of the acting group of Hitotsubashi High School…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169736,169736}…and whose talent is highly recognized by the critics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173340,173340}Next, we do not need an introduction\Nfro Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182949,182949}Last, but not least, Kitajima Maya\Nfrom Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190457,190457}The audition is set for August 8th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198031,198031}Ayumi, is it true that you moved\Nout of your mother's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201101,201101}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203503,203503}Why? You can get advice from\Nyour mother, should you live with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207674,207674}That's right. And you can practice for "The Miracle Worker" together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213513,213513}That's the reason\NI moved out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216583,216583}I don't need my mother's reputation to get this role.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219853,219853}I will win this role solely with my talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:42.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222789,222789}Ayumi,\Nwhat a strict person you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:49.22,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:229229,229229}"The Miracle Worker" is an inspiring and touching drama about a girl Helen Keller, who can't hear, see, nor speak but comes to understand words through Ms. Sullivan's passionate and persistent education.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:09.81,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:249816,249816}When school got out for summer break, Maya started practicing everyday at the church with Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255588,255588}Sit still and eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257657,257657}Fold the napkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260894,260894}Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262595,262595}Wait, Helen!\NHelen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265899,265899}Don't run away from me.\NYou are not done eating yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270837,270837}Helen, come back…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275842,275842}Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277911,277911}Why did you look at me, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280947,280947}Helen can not hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287387,287387}Here, Maya, become Helen now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291991,291991}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294394,294394}Walk as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296596,296596}Get mad as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:04:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298765,298765}Eat as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300500,300500}Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303370,303370}Now, Maya, play as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307407,307407}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309342,309342}Now, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:13.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313380,313380}Play as Helen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:14.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314681,314681}Play as Helen, who is blind, deaf,\Nand not able to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320153,320153}If you can't do that, you will never\Nknow the real Helen. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325658,325658}Teacher, that's enough.\NI can practice with her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332032,332032}Yeah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334634,334634}What?\NYou're tearing the church down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336936,336936}Yeah, haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339539,339539}A mansion is going to be built here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342542,342542}No way.\NThis is our practice hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351251,351251}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356723,356723}What a patient she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:05:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359793,359793}If she continues like this,\Nshe'll never get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:04.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364964,364964}Teacher is ill,\Nand the practice hall is gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:08.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368902,368902}What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389789,389789}I have a report about the five\Ncandidates for Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392959,392959}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395662,395662}Shiratori Reina is getting\Nstrict training at her theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404637,404637}Hayakawa Akiko is actually playing\NHelen Keller with her acting group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411644,411644}Kanaya Emi is in libraries\Ndoing research about Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416282,416282}And Himekawa Ayumi is volunteering at an agency for disabled children like Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424257,424257}As for Kitajima Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428895,428895}…the church she was practicing at was demolished and now she doesn't have anywhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451084,451084}Maya, Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452852,452852}Look, it's Mr. Purple Rose again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453053,453053}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:38.79,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:458792,458792}Ms. Kitajima Maya
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462062,462062}"I believe it's hot in Tōkyō now."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464364,464364}"If it's not too much, I would like to invite you to my summer house in Nagano."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468435,468435}Summer house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472005,472005}Wow, there's a train ticket, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477377,477377}I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:07:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479813,479813}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482515,482515}I'll go and practice\NHelen's role there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:07.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487120,487120}"I will not be able to be there,\Nbut my friends will look after you."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:16.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496129,496129}Mr. Purple Rose always helps\Nme out whenever I'm in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:20.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500166,500166}He's like my guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:31.67,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:511678,511678}Bidoro
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512679,512679}Hey, Sakurakōji.\NYou should have came a day earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515815,515815}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517050,517050}You know, Mr. Purple Rose.\NShe got an invitation from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:49.46,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529462,529462}Maya, I can't do anything\Nfor you, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544310,544310}How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547514,547514}Hi there, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549983,549983}I'm Yamashita, the house sitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553386,553386}I'm Kitajima Maya.\NIt's very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556656,556656}Here, come on in.\NWe've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563229,563229}Wow, it's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565131,565131}It's bright and has\Na beautiful view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568001,568001}Yes, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570036,570036}We live right down the street, so please don't hesitate to come to us if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575108,575108}Of course, we'll come by to clean and prepare meals, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578812,578812}Oh, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581114,581114}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583216,583216}What is the owner of this house like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588321,588321}Oh, by the way, he told us to give you the flowers there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:09:59.83,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:599833,599833}Ms. Kitajima Maya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601134,601134}"I hope you will have\Na wonderful time."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604337,604337}"I do have one wish:\Nplease don't ask around about me."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611411,611411}"—Mr. Purple Rose."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:22.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622722,622722}I understand.\NI won't ask about you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:26.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626393,626393}I will win Helen's role here.
Comment: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:45.72,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:645728,645728}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:49.52,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:649524,649524}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:52.48,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:652485,652485}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656222,656222}Did you sleep well last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:10:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658491,658491}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660393,660393}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662462,662462}It's a nice day today.\NYou should go outside and play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665965,665965}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667233,667233}A young girl should not stay home all day. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670303,670303}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683983,683983}A yacht and a sailboat,\Nhorse back riding and cycling…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687620,687620}I'm sure Helen\Ndidn't play this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692092,692092}Teacher, I suggest we take turns\Ngetting off work to go see Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697397,697397}I'm sure it's hard\Nto practice without a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701434,701434}No, being Helen\Ndoesn't require a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705605,705605}She's better off by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708375,708375}By herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712979,712979}Yes.\NAll by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:11:58.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718818,718818}Helen… I still don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:02.85,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722856,722856}What was your everyday life like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:05.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725558,725558}How did you spend a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:10.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730797,730797}Helen…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:13.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733600,733600}Helen's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739673,739673}I got it.\NI'll live as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:25.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745912,745912}Some cotton…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:30.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750684,750684}…and some dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:33.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753653,753653}Helen's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:36.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756956,756956}I'll live as Helen,\Nin the darkness and silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777143,777143}Maya, Maya.\NMaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:12:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779546,779546}It's strange, dear.\NAll the windows are closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783450,783450}Here, let me have the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784718,784718}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790123,790123}It's dark in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792359,792359}Maya, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796863,796863}Oh!\NWhat the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805572,805572}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805772,805772}Upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825392,825392}Ma-Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830263,830263}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:52.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832565,832565}Who?\NA touch, but whose hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:02.34,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842342,842342}Oh, the caretakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845245,845245}What's wrong, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847013,847013}What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854120,854120}Do · not · wo·rry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858925,858925}This · is · prac·tice · for · my · act·ing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875842,875842}Say, dear, she says not to worry,\Nbut do you think she's really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880246,880246}Maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:43.01,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883016,883016}They came,\Nthat means morning is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:47.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887654,887654}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:37.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937804,937804}Here it is!\NThe fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:08.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968501,968501}I wonder what time it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:10.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970637,970637}Night, or day?\NOr morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:15.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975709,975709}Many thoughts come\Nto me as I sit like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:20.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980613,980613}Sakurakōji.\NHow is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:23.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983917,983917}Teacher and Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:25.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985885,985885}It feels so long\Nsince I last saw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:33.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993293,993293}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:35.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995128,995128}You have been missing,\Nbut where are you, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024391,1024391}Business is well this summer,\Nhuh, Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028128,1028128}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030230,1030230}This party of yours, with many\Ncelebrities from Metropolitan Entertainment…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033066,1033066}…has become a popular tradition in Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038438,1038438}It's good advertisement for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040974,1040974}Many big names from the economic and political worlds are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043977,1043977}So, as artists, your reputation shall surely flourish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050717,1050717}You make anyone a tool of your business, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056022,1056022}Do you have anyone without business ties?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059292,1059292}Him?\NOf course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063029,1063029}You'll choose a woman with the most advantages for your business for your future wife, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068501,1068501}What, are you drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068935,1068935}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071438,1071438}I will be very careful in choosing,\Neven using a computer if I have to…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074274,1074274}…for a person who is suitable\Nfor Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077610,1077610}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079713,1079713}Mr. Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080146,1080146}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081981,1081981}The house sitter of your summer house\Nwants to see you immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090623,1090623}I've never seen him lose his cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:33.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113380,1113380}I knew to be careful\Nwhen coming down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:39.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119619,1119619}Ouch!\NI can't stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:41.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121821,1121821}I must have sprained my ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:44.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124090,1124090}I wonder how long\NI've been doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:46.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126793,1126793}Yet I still can't learn her ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:48.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128795,1128795}Helen's life, Helen's play…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:52.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132265,1132265}I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:54.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134134,1134134}I want to take the earplugs\Nand blindfold off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:57.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137203,1137203}I want to hear, see and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:00.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140407,1140407}I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:03.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143576,1143576}I'm taking this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:11.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151051,1151051}No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:13.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153286,1153286}I will never understand\Nhow Helen feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:18.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158491,1158491}Whatever happens, I will stay\Nlike this until I learn her ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:36.34,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176343,1176343}Who?\NWhose hand is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:38.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178278,1178278}Not the caretaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:42.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182582,1182582}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:52.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192258,1192258}Oh, a rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:19:58.33,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198331,1198331}It's a rose.\NMr. Purple Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:04.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204137,1204137}Are · you · Mr. · Pur·ple · Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:30.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230030,1230030}Finally!\NI finally get to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:33.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233833,1233833}The person who has been encouraging me ever since my first stage appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:40.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240874,1240874}The person who is always on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:43.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243877,1243877}Thank you.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:46.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246880,1246880}Little girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:03.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263797,1263797}What was that?\NHe just held me and…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281581,1281581}W-Wait!\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285018,1285018}Please tell me, just your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287120,1287120}I appreciate you with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290123,1290123}Every time I'm about to give up,\NI always think about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293827,1293827}Please, please tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302202,1302202}I · am · look·ing · for·ward\Nto · see·ing · your · Hel·en.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317017,1317017}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:07.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327660,1327660}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.63,0:22:11.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331631,1331631}Something's wrong with you,\NHayami Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:13.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333767,1333767}She's a girl more than ten years\Nyounger than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:16.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1336670,1336670}Being the person that I am,\Nbeing the person that I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:20.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340907,1340907}I am looking forward\Nto seeing your Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:23.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343643,1343643}I am looking forward\Nto seeing your Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:27.34,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347347,1347347}I'll do it.\NI won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:30.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350283,1350283}I'll become Helen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:34.88,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1354888,1354888}Maya has finally met\NMr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:37.75,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1357757,1357757}It was a mysterious meeting, but it became an inspiration for Maya, who struggles to understand Helen.
